      <h1>Child Tax Credit 2025: Amount, Rules, and Who Qualifies</h1>
      <p>The 2025 Child Tax Credit is worth up to $2,000 per qualifying child under age 17. Up to $1,700 per child is refundable through the Additional Child Tax Credit. The credit phases out starting at $200,000 of modified AGI ...</p>
